code:
sequenceDiagram
    participant Passenger
    participant BookingService
    participant Driver
    participant PaymentService
    participant RatingService

    Passenger->>BookingService: createRideRequest()
    BookingService-->>Passenger: RideRequest(PENDING)

    BookingService->>Driver: match driver & vehicle
    Driver-->>BookingService: accepts ride
    BookingService-->>Passenger: Ride(STARTED)

    Driver->>BookingService: completes ride
    BookingService-->>Passenger: Ride(COMPLETED)

    Passenger->>PaymentService: payFare()
    PaymentService-->>Passenger: Payment(SUCCESS)

    Passenger->>RatingService: rateRide()
    RatingService-->>Driver: Rating saved
